criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age between 18 and 75 years;

          -  duration of PD (automated peritoneal dialysis (APD) or continuous ambulatory
             peritoneal dialysis (CAPD)) >4 weeks

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe heart failure (New York Heart Association Functional Classification; NYHA III
             or IV);

          -  pregnancy;

          -  catheter malfunction or

          -  peritonitis within 3 months prior to the trial.
